SUMMARY:FULT — Small Group Call #3
DESCRIPTION:Reach out to your dealer to confirm timing and availability\n\n
 Small group investor call\nIssuer: FULTON FINL CORP (FULT)\n\nDeal context
 :\nFulton Financial Corporation is conducting fixed income investor calls 
 on April 29-30\, organized by Piper Sandler and J.P. Morgan\, ahead of a p
 otential subordinated notes offering. Subject to market conditions\, the h
 olding company plans an SEC-registered offering of subordinated notes with
  expected ratings of Baa2 (Moody's) and BBB(high) (Morningstar DBRS)\, pla
 cing the deal firmly in Investment Grade territory. No size\, tenor\, or p
 ricing details have been disclosed at this mandate stage\, with Piper Sand
 ler coordinating logistics for the investor calls.
